                            <comment id="12941056" author="gseben" created="Tue, 24 Mar 2009 16:32:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch for the issue is attached.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that, the selectNodeIterator check is still attempted to maintain previous functionality. In the case of selecting an empty element selectNodeIterator would return true while eval() returns false. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix adds more flexibility to the XPath expressions that can be used and SelectorTest.java was update to to test a wider range of comparisons.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
